  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Starship</span>. This fighter craft is armed with a powerful <span class=\"name name-technology\">Positron Ejector</span> for rapid destruction of hostile ships.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，这艘战斗飞船装备了强大的<span class=\"name name-technology\">正电子冲击波</span>，能够快速摧毁敌方飞船。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一艘特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>。這艘戰鬥太空船裝備強大的<span class=\"name name-technology\">正電子發射器</span>，能夠快速摧毀敵對太空船。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，可利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
